<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Tradeboard</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A073F0 0%, #8A5CF5 100%);
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 32px;
        }

        .welcome-message, .role-section {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .welcome-message p, .role-section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .name {
            color: #A073F0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #A073F0;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 24px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #8A5CF5;
        }

        .support-message {
            padding: 24px;
            background: #f8f5ff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #A073F0;
            margin: 32px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            background: #f5f5f7;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #86868b;
        }

        /* Animation for container */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .animate {
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 24px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container animate">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://test.tradeboard.in/images/Tradeboard_logo_RGB.png" alt="Tradeboard Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Welcome to Tradeboard</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <p>Hello {{partnerName}},</p>
                <p>You have been added as an accountability partner for <span class="name">{{userName}}</span> in their trading journey with Tradeboard.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="role-section">
                <p>As an accountability partner, you will receive {{frequency}} updates on <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>'s trading performance. These updates will help you support and encourage <span class="name">{{userName}}</span> in their trading goals.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Your role as an accountability partner is crucial in helping traders stay motivated and disciplined. We appreciate your commitment to supporting <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>.</p>
            
            <p>
                <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">View Dashboard</a>
            </p>
            
            <div class="support-message">
                <p>If you have any questions about your role or the updates you'll receive, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Thank you for being a part of the Tradeboard community!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>